# SociallyFounded - Current Website Analysis

This document provides a detailed analysis of the current SociallyFounded website as of May 2025, serving as a reference point for future development.

## Overview

The current website consists of two main pages:
- Homepage (index.html)
- About page (about.html)
- Thank you page (thanks.html)

The site uses a consistent color scheme, typography, and design language across all pages.

## Visual Design Elements

### Color Palette
- Navy Blue: #003554 (primary brand color)
- White: #FFFFFF
- Light Gray: #F5F5F5 (background)
- Accent Gray: #E0E0E0

### Typography
- Font Family: 'Poppins', sans-serif
- Heading Sizes:
  - h1: 38px (mobile: 28px)
  - h2: 28px (mobile: 24px)
  - h3: 22px (mobile: 20px)
- Body Text: 17px (mobile: 16px)

### Layout
- Responsive design with mobile and desktop breakpoints
- Container max-width: 1200px
- Two-column layout on desktop (content | form)
- Single-column layout on mobile

### UI Components
- Buttons: Navy background, white text, 10px border-radius
- Forms: Light borders, 10px border-radius
- Cards: White background, subtle shadows, rounded corners

